)

Subj1:"Mathematics"/Chap1:"Work Problems"/Topi1:"Combined Work"/Type1:"A"/Diff1:"E"/Stem1:""/(
Q:"If A completes a particular work in 8 days and B the same work in 24 days. How many days will it take if they work together?"
A:"c"
O:a)"4",b)"5",c)"6",d)"7"
R:"1/8 + 1/24 = 4/24 = 1/6 → 6 days."
)

Subj1:"Mathematics"/Chap1:"Sequences"/Topi1:"Pattern"/Type1:"U"/Diff1:"M"/Stem1:""/(
Q:"What comes next in the sequence: 1, 3, 11, 43, ______?"
A:"b"
O:a)"161",b)"171",c)"181",d)"191"
R:"Pattern: multiply by 4 and subtract 1: 1×4−1=3, 3×4−1=11, 11×4−1=43, 43×4−1=171."
)

Subj1:"Mathematics"/Chap1:"Speed Distance Time"/Topi1:"Distance"/Type1:"A"/Diff1:"E"/Stem1:""/(
