R:"80 × 3.5 = 280 km."
)

Subj1:"Mathematics"/Chap1:"Percentages"/Topi1:"Population"/Type1:"A"/Diff1:"E"/Stem1:""/(
Q:"In a class of 40 students 20% are girls. How many boys are there in the class?"
A:"d"
O:a)"26",b)"28",c)"30",d)"32"
R:"Girls = 8, boys = 40-8=32."
)